OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,7,Fpraised the "Herculean efforts" to
OL,8,Fprotect people from the Kent
OL,9,Fmeningitis outbreak and care for those
OL,10,Faffected.
OL,12,FThe number of cases of meningitis
OL,13,Flinked to an outbreak in Kent has
OL,14,Fdropped as the campaign to vaccinate
OL,15,Fthousands of young people continues
OL,16,Finto a fourth day.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@_O]
