OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FConfirmed cases have fallen from 23 to
OL,7,F20, the UK Health Security Agency
OL,8,F(UKHSA) said in an update on Sunday
OL,9,Fmorning, after they were downgraded
OL,10,Ffollowing further testing.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, suspected cases under
OL,13,Finvestigation have also fallen from 11
OL,14,Fto nine, meaning the total number of
OL,15,Fcases is 29, down from 34 on Saturday.
OL,17,FNineteen of the 20 confirmed cases are
OL,18,Fmeningitis B and all cases have
OL,19,Frequired hospital admission.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
