OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FOne of the suspected cases has been
OL,7,Flinked to a second Kent academic
OL,8,Finstitution, to join University of
OL,9,FKent.
OL,11,FEast Kent Colleges (EKC) Group sent
OL,12,Fout a letter to all parents and carers
OL,13,Finforming them that a college student
OL,14,Fwas being treated for a suspected case
OL,15,Fof meningitis on Friday, and published
OL,16,Fthe letter on their website on Sunday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
