OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FMr Streeting offered his condolences
OL,7,Fto the families of the two students
OL,8,Fwho have died in the outbreak and said
OL,9,Fhis thoughts are with those in
OL,10,Fhospital "fighting this terrible
OL,11,Fdisease".
OL,13,FHe said in the statement on Sunday:
OL,14,F"It has been an incredibly difficult
OL,15,Fweek for those affected and for those
OL,16,Fworking on the frontline response to
OL,17,Fthis outbreak.
OL,26,@rD@JOUsD@HO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"As we look ahead to another
OL,7,Fchallenging week, I wanted to pay
OL,8,Ftribute to the Herculean efforts of
OL,9,Feveryone who has worked tirelessly to
OL,10,Fcare for those affected and keep
OL,11,Fpeople safe."
OL,13,FThe Health Secretary thanked UKHSA
OL,14,Fofficials and NHS teams, as well as
OL,15,Fschool, college and university staff,
OL,16,Fand the "thousands of students, pupils
OL,17,Fand other members of the public who
OL,18,Fhave so readily and responsibly come
OL,19,Fforward for antibiotics and
OL,20,Fvaccination".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@MO]xD@IOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
