PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FIt came after dozens of eligible
OL,7,Fpeople, including students, queued up
OL,8,Fagain around the county for the menB
OL,9,Fvaccine or antibiotics, although
OL,10,Fnumbers in the lines have dropped
OL,11,Fconsiderably since the rollout began
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, with no queue outside
OL,13,Fthe previously busy University of Kent
OL,14,FCanterbury campus vaccination site as
OL,15,Fof 10am on Sunday.
OL,17,FThe UKHSA said it expects more cases
OL,18,Fto be downgraded in the coming days as
OL,19,Ffurther laboratory assessments are
OL,20,Fcompleted.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
