FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FDr Sherine Thomas, infectious diseases
OL,7,Fconsultant at the UKHSA, said: "We
OL,8,Fcontinue to remain vigilant for new
OL,9,Fcases and work closely with NHS
OL,10,FEngland and local authorities across
OL,11,Fthe country to ensure that any new
OL,12,Fcases identified are responded to as
OL,13,Fquickly as possible.
OL,15,F"It's reassuring to have seen so many
OL,16,Feligible young people come forward for
OL,17,Fantibiotics and vaccination, and we'd
OL,18,Flike to thank everyone involved in
OL,19,Fthis effort so far.
OL,26,@oD@`OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1774285870
OL,3,CHealth Secretary praises 'Herculean
OL,4,Cefforts' in Kent meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"Although the risk to the wider
OL,7,Fpopulation remains low, it is still
OL,8,Freally important that people know the
OL,9,Fsymptoms of invasive meningococcal
OL,10,Fdisease and seek immediate medical
OL,11,Fattention if they or anyone they know
OL,12,Fdevelops them. UKHSA continues to work
OL,13,Fwith partners to identify contacts and
OL,14,Foffer necessary treatment."
OL,16,FNHS Kent and Medway said more than
OL,17,F9,078 meningitis B vaccines had been
OL,18,Fhanded out as of Saturday evening
OL,19,Fwhile 12,595 antibiotics had been
OL,20,Fadministered.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
